{"tid":943182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]交友App色情資訊氾濫　8.4%中學生收過裸照","createTime":"2018-12-16T10:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T12:18:25.000Z","uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8708fbb37e79dc1c8a00d6b960fb8f385c49820","tid":943182,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"青少年熱愛使用交友應用程式溝通，但網上交友其實危機重重。關注傳媒對青少年影響聯席於今年5至6月對1900名中學生進行有關交友應用程式影響的調查，發現15.9%人曾遭欺凌，另有不少學生收過色情訊息，9.2%人曾收過性感照片，8.4%人收過裸體照，5.6%人更曾收過性邀請。 <br />\n<br />\n受訪稱曾受欺凌的學生，主要受言語攻擊佔33.2%，照片被公開或改圖佔4%，自由脈搏通識研究中心總監陳鑑銘指，有14.2%受訪者曾欺凌他人，當中不少人曾被欺凌，顯示兩者有惡性循環關係。他指，調查發現的欺凌數字可能只是冰山一角，估計不少人不敢發聲或不自覺被欺凌。 <br />\n<br />\n調查亦顯示不少青少年曾收到色情訊息，8.4%人收過裸體照，4.3%被人要求傳送性感照。基督教女青年會督導主任蘇艷芳表示，很多青少年認為網上交友「唔會蝕底」，對身體的保護意識亦不高，在網上交換性感照的青少年最年幼只有12、13歲。調查中亦有22.5%人曾約網友見面，蘇指青少年會與網友約會易發生性侵事件，籲他們約網友前先與相熟的成人商討。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181216/photo/bkn-20181216162336597-1216_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181216175903\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181216%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181216162336597-1216_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181216175903&h=5e4c134a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調查發現8.4%中學生使用交友應用程式曾收過裸體照。(趙韻清攝)"},{"pid":"4af657a80679ce349be2da54e95da1c3759d46ae","tid":943182,"uid":205976,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"這不叫有圖"},{"pid":"b3392415490949f3832e9faae49a8b23aaa6dd6d","tid":943182,"uid":61543,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4af657a80679ce349be2da54e95da1c3759d46ae","tid":943182,"uid":205976,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"這不叫有圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"趙韻清攝"},{"pid":"414928c1ff63ed7721e7da73984adf2deb663178","tid":943182,"uid":134323,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"查調亦發現91.6中學生講大話"},{"pid":"a4f233008f8a7160984110c70f99ccea283e23ae","tid":943182,"uid":166725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c53e4deaa537b2721a1f69fafb086ded62200b","tid":943182,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"小學生都識睇av啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f15fe09c631f3a971e40f46d7db8704d09c5aa","tid":943182,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:02:48.000Z","msg":"點解我未收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a785d61c1f8da1fb13be045dd2adda0ab1d30627","tid":943182,"uid":13448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"小學生已經仆緊野喇 咩年代<br />\n揾處要去幼稚園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b1e8257bcf0d8af073ef36a6a9df917f58332c","tid":943182,"uid":55224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"交乜撚友app姐 約炮app就叫約炮app啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你估班中學雞真係0機心咁用個app既咩"}]}